author: glyn
msg: Make DefaultEngineConfigurationFactory the standard way to obtain
engine configurations. This is overrideable and configurable via
Java system properties. Further flexibility in how configurations
are built may be required in the future, but it should now be
possible to implemented them using localised changes.
since no other Axis code should need to know these values.
